---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Xiaohongshu AI Operator">
  <section class="grid gap-10 py-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-rose-400/30 bg-rose-400/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-rose-200">
        AI digital content operator for Xiaohongshu creators
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">
        给小红书创作者的
        <span class="text-rose-300">AI 数字运营人</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-300">
        不只是帮你写一篇文案，而是帮你持续完成账号画像、竞品拆解、选题池、Note Brief、草稿、审核和发布计划。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/dashboard"
          class="rounded-full bg-rose-400 px-6 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-neutral-950 hover:bg-rose-300"
        >
          打开 MVP Dashboard
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/XingMXTeam/xiaohongshushipfast"
          class="rounded-full border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          查看 GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-rose-950/30">
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">MVP workflow</p>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
        {[
          "账号画像",
          "竞品研究",
          "选题池",
          "Note Brief",
          "草稿生成",
          "人工审核",
          "发布计划",
        ].map((step, index) => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900/80 p-4">
            <span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-rose-400/15 text-sm text-rose-200">
              {index + 1}
            </span>
            <span class="font-medium">{step}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid gap-4 py-10 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">不是 AI 写作工具</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-300">
        写文案只是最后一步。真正要解决的是每天不知道发什么、没有选题池、缺少复盘和审核标准。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">不是全自动代运营</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-300">
        MVP 保留人工审核节点。AI 负责推进流程，人负责判断品味、边界和最终发布。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">是可复用工作流</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-300">
        借鉴 agent-workstation 思路，把内容运营拆成可追踪、可调试、可复用的 Agent workflow。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500/10 to-purple-500/10 p-8">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-rose-200">Target users</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold">先服务一类真实用户</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <p class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-950/60 p-4 text-neutral-200">个人 IP：知道自己要做内容，但坚持不下来。</p>
        <p class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-950/60 p-4 text-neutral-200">本地商家：想做小红书获客，但不想招全职运营。</p>
        <p class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-950/60 p-4 text-neutral-200">小团队：代运营太贵，自己又缺系统方法。</p>
        <p class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-950/60 p-4 text-neutral-200">AI 初学者：想用 AI，但不知道如何真正落地到内容流程。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
